<h1 class="new-header">Rabbit Adoption Submission</h1>
<h3>
  As a shelter, we rely on our online community to send in any rabbits they may have
  for adoption. Our staff will review each submission and make the rabbits
  available for adoption. We thank each and every one of you for your contribution to the shelter.
</h3>

<form action="/rabbits" method="POST">
  Name: <input name="name" type="text" /><br />
  Image Link:<input name="img" type="text" /><br />
  Description: <input name="description" type="text" /><br />
  Age: <input name="age" type="text" /><br />
  Status: Pending <br />
  <div class="button-position"><input class="button" type="submit" value="Submit" /></div>
</form>

